d:"1",name:"Aarav Sharma",location:"Delhi",rating:5,text:"Best quality oversized tees! The cosmic designs are fire \ud83d\udd25 Ordered 3 more. Delivery was super fast to Delhi!",image:"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1669059921524-327a4c52cff3"},{id:"2",name:"Priya Reddy",location:"Hyderabad",rating:5,text:"Love the crop tops! Perfect fit and amazing quality. The zodiac collection is my favorite. Totally worth it! \u2728",image:"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1653875842174-429c1b467548"},{id:"3",name:"Rohan Patel",location:"Mumbai",rating:5,text:"Finally found the perfect streetwear brand in India! Quality is top-notch and prices are reasonable. Cosmic World is the GOAT! \ud83d\ude80",image:"https://images.pexels.com/photos/7945666/pexels-photo-7945666.jpeg"},{id:"4",name:"Diya Krishnan",location:"Bangalore",rating:5,text:"Obsessed with my new hoodies! The oversized fit is perfect. Everyone asks me where I got them from. Cosmic World all the way! \ud83d\udc9c",image:"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1772130204516-2145cc1402b7"}],En=[{id:"1",title:"10 Must-Have Streetwear Trends for Indian Gen Z in 2024",slug:"streetwear-trends-india-2024",category:"Fashion Trends",excerpt:"Discover the hottest streetwear trends taking over India's Gen Z fashion scene. From oversized tees to cosmic prints.",image:"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542847957-80a6beffcbde",author:"Cosmic World Team",date:"2024-12-01",readTime:"5 min read",content:"Indian Gen Z is redefining streetwear with bold choices and cosmic vibes. Here are the top trends dominating 2024...",tags:["streetwear","gen-z","fashion-trends","india","2024"]},{id:"2",title:"How to Style Oversized Tees: The Ultimate Gen Z Guide",slug:"style-oversized-tees-genz-guide",category:"Styling Tips",excerpt:"Master the art of styling oversized t-shirts with these expert tips for college, hangouts, and street style.",image:"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1758967820401-36e8b3a4e1a2",author:"Priya Mehta",date:"2024-11-28",r